data.description: Motivated Seller! Looking for a spacious, affordable 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on a quiet street, then you need to see this one! This home sits on a large lot with a private back yard and mature trees. The interior has a neutral color scheme and is centrally located in the heart of Van Buren. All kitchen appliances convey, including refrigerator.
